title: Sun Sentinel Top 10: Broward football Week 9
text:
The Top 10 rankings remain steady this week after none of the Sun Sentinel Top 10 high school football teams suffered a loss coming out of Week 8 â€” for the first time all season.
There's a slim chance of the Top 10 going 10-0 again this week too, though Hallandale and Plantation may face challenges.
Each of this week's rankings is followed by the team's previous top-10 ranking, followed by the team and its record.
